Just wanted to mention something else also.  Not sure at 51 if the Librarian or the spell merchants near him will attack but if not you can skip the Lightstone quest and just hand him 4 stacks of 4 and then have somebody invis you before hitting trade.  Do that a few times and you should make indifferent.  Then just start doing the hand in yourself. <p><a href=http://eq.castersrealm.com/players/view_profile.asp?Id=58956>Zaknafinis Convoquer (55th Conjurer)</a>
